{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "17.1",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "75d52c8f",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "さて……では、スイカ割りをしますよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.1",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d9cb7d88",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "スイカ割り……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.1",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ec554504",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "スイカと呼ばれる果物……野菜？　野菜果物を砂浜に置き、目隠しをして破壊する遊戯です",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.1",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "422c192a",
      "speaker": "プリズム",
      "ja": "それは……なぜ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.1",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f44e28a8",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "なぜとは……海で行う遊びの定番だからです",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.1",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4ba4e4fa",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そうなの？　……何で果物を壊すの？　何でスイカ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.1",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7d10e81b",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "こわ……すのが楽しいからでは？　スイカである理由は……この気候が旬の作物だからかと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.0",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d6f87cdf",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "食べ物で遊ぶのは良くないぞ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.1",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "91c08375",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あーもう、やかましい！　いいからとっとと始めますよ！　ルミナ様の希望なのですから！　本で読んだ遊戯を１度行ってみたいと！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86590d65",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "はあ……いまいちイメージ湧かないけど、どうやるんだ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.0",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e7577ba6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こ……これが、すいか……？　果物なのか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.1",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6d7fc783",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "なんかエグい模様入ってるな……本当に食べられるのか？　病気とかじゃあ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.1",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b9201f00",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "我々の星では比較的ポピュラーな作物です。暑い環境で必要になる栄養素が多く、摂食を推奨されているのですよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.1",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c7ba90ed",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "へえ……美味しいといいけどな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.1",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f21e4990",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "甘くて美味しい、よ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.1",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6b82bf97",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "（この様子では、割って赤い中身が出てきた時に悲鳴が起きそうですね）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.1",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ba322075",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "よっしゃ！　とにかくやってみっか！　全員で目隠ししてスイカを囲んで、狙うのか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "66.1",
      "line_index": 66,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e4f127aa",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "そんなことしたら危険でしょう、見た目も、物理的にも。……挑戦する人を決めて、１人ずつ回すんですよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.1",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "98703fe0",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "じゃあ……誰から、する……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.1",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "43caf135",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "いきなり成功してもつまらないですから……機械士、行きなさい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8e4a48e3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺か！？　……いいけど",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "74.1",
      "line_index": 74,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cd3ea577",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "じゃあ、目隠しする……ね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.0",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5b3932d2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "これでいいのか？　案外簡単そうだな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.0",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "995812df",
      "speaker": "雫の声",
      "ja": "棒を持ち、10回体を回しなさい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.0",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "44f8717b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うっ……そう簡単じゃないか。わかった",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.0",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "96d1adb7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "頭の中で１０数えながら、体を回転させる。フラついてコケそうになったが、なんとか砂を踏みしめ耐えた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.0",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d69af482",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……意外と、これ、効くな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "51c8b250",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もうどちらを向いてるかわからない。ヘタをすれば海に突っ込んでしまいそうだ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.0",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86d1d78e",
      "speaker": "コハルの声",
      "ja": "それで、後は割ればいいの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.0",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f0bab4d7",
      "speaker": "雫の声",
      "ja": "全員で指示を出し、スイカまで導きます。ウソをついても構いません",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.0",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "52107500",
      "speaker": "コハルの声",
      "ja": "へー。ちょっとズレてるわ。左側向いて！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.0",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9ac9372c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こ、こうか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.0",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e2b0ce1c",
      "speaker": "ルミナの声",
      "ja": "行き過ぎ……だよ。ちょっと右に……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e4e95f8c",
      "speaker": "ブロワーの声",
      "ja": "いいな！　あんちゃん、そこから真っ直ぐだ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.0",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ac9929e4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "真っ直ぐ……と……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.0",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6bf9698",
      "speaker": "プリズムの声",
      "ja": "ま、まだまだ全然先ですよ～！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.0",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "63a0172e",
      "speaker": "コハルの声",
      "ja": "そろそろよ、準備しなさい！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.0",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9666505e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お、じゃあ振りかぶって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "148bde60",
      "speaker": "雫の声",
      "ja": "頭の上にスイカがあります。全力でご自分の頭に振り下ろしなさい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.0",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6f1f7793",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "無茶苦茶言うなよ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b291b80",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "……ん？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.0",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b5a88449",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "突如、妙な感覚。水着……というか、パンツをひっぱられているような……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "130.0",
      "line_index": 130,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "38a2d116",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "おい、触るのもオーケーなのか？　明らかに妨害だろ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.0",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "55200ce7",
      "speaker": "雫の声",
      "ja": "……まあ別に禁止はしてませんが、誰も触ってませんよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a1340e09",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "え？　で、でも……いいっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.0",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3d9036c0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "錯覚ではない。明らかに、腹……太もも……股間を掴まれている！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "141.0",
      "line_index": 141,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e663e99a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "や、やめろーっ！　く……くすぐったいっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.0",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21c302c1",
      "speaker": "雫の声",
      "ja": "何をいきなり暴れてるのです！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f731cbd1",
      "speaker": "ルミナの声",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}くん……！？　もしかして、パン……服に、何か入ったの……！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.0",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "37b6592",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いや……！　これは誰かが絶対、うひひっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6aab3e0e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……うぐわぁーっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.0",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "57dbfabf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "とうとうパンツが下ろされてしまい、慌てて座り込む。……体の前側は、海側に出来たのでセーフだと思いたい。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "169.1",
      "line_index": 169,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "bc4515b0",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "またこの変態男は……！　露出癖でもあるのですか！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.1",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8e21e32f",
      "speaker": "プリズム",
      "ja": "うーむ……見事な美しい桃……インスピレーションが湧いてきそうです",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "173.1",
      "line_index": 173,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "613d35fc",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そんなこと言ってないで、服、服！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.0",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e256370b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うう……す、すまんコハル……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.1",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9215a70f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "もう、やっぱり水着じゃなくて、パンツだけで泳ぐのは無理ね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "179.0",
      "line_index": 179,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5c01b646",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "泳いでないんだが……というか、誰が俺のパンツ下げたんだ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.1",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "50e6f3b3",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "誰も触ってないわよ！　……自然と落ちたんじゃないの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.0",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "522f71fb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そんなはずないんだけどな……目閉じてたから、風が手の感触に感じたのか……？　いやまさか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.1",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8bb3beb9",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "はいはい、次はおいらだな！　あんちゃん、目隠し寄越しな！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.0",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "16cdb1bd",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う、うお！　ちょっと待ってくれ！　まだ着替えてない……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "204.0",
      "line_index": 204,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "da3efd9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ブロワーが目隠しと棒を受取り、嬉々として所定の位置で回転を始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "206.0",
      "line_index": 206,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cc90dffc",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "石の声で楽勝、とか無いよな……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "208.1",
      "line_index": 208,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8c246619",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "あー大丈夫大丈夫、聞こうと思わなきゃ聞こえないし、ここらへん砂ばっかだし！　よし、行くぞー！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "210.0",
      "line_index": 210,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e9b7660",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ブロワーが回転を終え、スイカに向かって歩き始める。迷いがない歩きに一瞬見えているのではと思ったが、微妙にルートが外れ始めた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "225.0",
      "line_index": 225,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "34d6358f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ブロワー！　もうちょっと左だ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "227.1",
      "line_index": 227,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b7eef9a5",
      "speaker": "プリズム",
      "ja": "あと１５歩くらい先ですよ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "229.1",
      "line_index": 229,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fa8b0cf",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "そのまま……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "231.0",
      "line_index": 231,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b40da4c9",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（……なんか、皆ホントの事言っててちょっと悔しいな。でも方向とかのウソをついたらバレるかも知れないから……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "233.0",
      "line_index": 233,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "76fa3810",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "足元！　大きい石があるからちょっと避けたほうがいいぞ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "243.1",
      "line_index": 243,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2988b4cb",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "……あんちゃん、おいらに石があるってウソは流石に通用しないぞ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "245.0",
      "line_index": 245,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bb63e553",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……あ、そっか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "247.1",
      "line_index": 247,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f641280c",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "ははは！　後で覚えとけよ～？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "249.0",
      "line_index": 249,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aad9d3db",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ぐっ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "251.0",
      "line_index": 251,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a628ad0a",
      "speaker": "プリズムの声",
      "ja": "そこです！　ブロワーさん、振り下ろしてください！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "254.1",
      "line_index": 254,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a857b90",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "おっしゃあ！　せーのっ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "265.1",
      "line_index": 265,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3e023d12",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "おわっ！　冷たっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "267.0",
      "line_index": 267,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b26af44a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "へ……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "269.0",
      "line_index": 269,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87b857b4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "スイカが割れて、中から果汁が噴き出る。……というか、飛び散る？　スイカは跡形もなく消失し、無色の果汁は砂へと染み込んでいった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "280.0",
      "line_index": 280,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d785f708",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんか……水みたいな果汁だな。果肉も無いのか、スイカって？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "282.1",
      "line_index": 282,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fcabae2d",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "水みたいというか……水ですね、これは。どういうことでしょうか、これは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "284.1",
      "line_index": 284,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5eb2868",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "スイカが……消え、ちゃった……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "286.0",
      "line_index": 286,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b3a3fdee",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、これおかしい事なのか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "288.1",
      "line_index": 288,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1225816f",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "あたりまえでしょう。割ったら消える果物がどこにありますか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "290.1",
      "line_index": 290,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c43dbece",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "ううん……ブロワー、さん。大丈夫……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "292.1",
      "line_index": 292,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "878a9fd0",
      "speaker": "ブロワー",
      "ja": "ああ。濡れただけだしな。……くんくん。変な匂いも味もしないから、ただの水じゃないか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "294.0",
      "line_index": 294,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5b9e482a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うかつに舐めるなよ、そんな謎の水……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "296.1",
      "line_index": 296,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "566d1976",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "……？　どこいっちゃったんだろう、スイカ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "298.1",
      "line_index": 298,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2a73799",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "目にも止まらぬ速さで吹き飛んだとか……？　それでは水の説明が……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "300.0",
      "line_index": 300,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f2d4ca8f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "首をひねるルミナ達だったが、いくら考えても答えが出ないため、諦めて次のスイカを持ってくるのだった……",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
